## What belongs here vs. in the domain

| Concern | Where it lives |
|---|---|
| DB column ↔ domain field mapping | `toDomain` / `toCreateInput` / `toUpdateInput` |
| Prisma `where` / `orderBy` clauses | `toFilterWhere` / `defaultOrderBy` |
| Transaction logic (`$transaction`) | Repository subclass, using `this.$transaction(...)` |
| Business rules (invariant checks) | Domain aggregate method — never the repository |
| External HTTP calls | Port adapter (`infrastructure/http/`) |
| Message broker publish | Messaging producer (`infrastructure/messaging/`) |
| Message broker subscribe | Messaging consumer → delegates to use case |
| Caching | Repository or port adapter wrapper (`infrastructure/cache/`) |
| Error mapping (HTTP/broker → domain) | Infrastructure adapter — must map before throwing |
